The '''Sisar Runners''' were a branch of the [[Hutt underground]], led by [[Embra]], that operated during the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]]. In [[29 ABY/Legends|29 ABY]] the Runners aided the [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]] in preparation for the retaking of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. They were probably named for the [[Sisar Run/Legends|Sisar Run]], which was a [[Hyperspace route/Legends|hyperlane]] located within the [[Periphery/Legends|Periphery]], situated near [[Hutt Space/Legends|Hutt Space]].

